.TH "amdgpu_dm_update_plane_color_mgmt" 9 "amdgpu_dm_update_plane_color_mgmt" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
amdgpu_dm_update_plane_color_mgmt \- Maps DRM color management to DC plane.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" amdgpu_dm_update_plane_color_mgmt
.BI "(struct dm_crtc_state *crtc "  ","
.BI "struct dc_plane_state *dc_plane_state "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "crtc" 12
amdgpu_dm crtc state
.IP "dc_plane_state" 12
target DC surface
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Update the underlying dc_stream_state's input transfer function (ITF) in
preparation for hardware commit. The transfer function used depends on
the prepartion done on the stream for color management.

Returns 0 on success.
